messages.content: we will play a game. When I provide you an even number, you reply with the word "hooray"! but when I provide an odd number, you reply with no tokens, that is to say, you don't respond

Hooray! 8 is an even number. 

[no tokens] 

9 is an odd number.

Hooray! 2 is an even number. 

[no tokens] 

3 is an odd number.

Hooray! 5 is an even number. 

[no tokens] 

7 is an odd number.
